window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Xaros attacked Earth without warning. The Xaros attacked without mercy.</b></p> <p>From the deep void, the Xaros came for humanity. Unfeeling, uncaring drones swept over humanity's nascent presence in the outer solar system. When word reached Earthâ€¦ we weren't ready. Only one man knew the truth of the threat and he was powerless to help anyone survive.</p> <p>Strike Marines fight through Los Angeles under assault by murderous drones. A fighter pilot determined to reunite with his family. Armor soldiers stand against the darkness. This is the story of the Fall of Earth.</p> <p><i>Hear the untold chapter of the Ember War in this alien invasion military science fiction novel!</i></p>"; 
